snippet.title: Super Nintendo Entertainment System™: Super NES Classic Edition Features Trailer
snippet.description:
The Super Nintendo Entertainment System™: Super NES Classic Edition has the original look and feel, only smaller, and pre-loaded with 21 games!

Available September 29th! https://goo.gl/2MG9iZ

#SNES #SuperNESClassicEdition
